data.description: Looking for a home perfect for entertaining, conveniently located in city limits, and at the end of a quiet cul-de-sac?? Well, look no further!! This very well maintained house in the desirable Bluff Estates subdivision hosts 4 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms with a basement that could serve as a 5th bedroom or second family room area!! Open floor plan, large master bedroom, a breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances, double garage, and a fenced in back yard with raised deck all make this a must see! Schedule your showing today, this one won't last long!!!
